'''雷克斯堡'''（{{lang-en|Rexburg}}）是[[美國|美國]][[愛達荷州|愛達荷州]][[麥迪遜縣_(愛達荷州)|麥迪遜郡]]的一個城市。據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，雷克斯堡有人口25,484人，比2000年的17,257人增長<ref name=quickfacts>{{cite web | url = http://quickfacts.census.gov/qfd/states/16/1667420.html | title = Quickfacts: Rexburg, Idaho | publisher = [[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]], Population Division | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2011-12-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118053331/http://quickfacts.census.gov/qfd/states/16/1667420.html | archive-date = 2016-01-18 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。雷克斯堡是麥迪遜郡的郡治<ref name="GR6">{{cite web|url=http://www.naco.org/Counties/Pages/FindACounty.aspx|accessdate=2011-06-07|title=Find a County|publisher=National Association of Counties|archive-date=2012-07-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6962cjXgL?url=http://www.naco.org/Counties/Pages/FindACounty.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是該縣最大的城市<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=7053|title= Profile for Rexburg, Idaho, ID|publisher= ePodunk|accessdate= 2012-09-02|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120206031959/http://www.epodunk.com/cgi-bin/genInfo.php?locIndex=7053|archive-date= 2012-02-06|dead-url= yes}}</ref>。

